WEBVTT

00:08:58.695 --> 00:09:01.303
consult it and put it back in
on the left-hand side.

00:09:01.327 --> 00:09:04.608
As a result, the documents would be
ordered from left to right

00:09:04.632 --> 00:09:06.393
by how recently they had been used.

00:09:06.417 --> 00:09:09.191
And he found he could quickly find
what he was looking for

00:09:09.215 --> 00:09:11.269
by starting at the left-hand
side of the box

00:09:11.293 --> 00:09:12.865
and working his way to the right.

00:09:13.215 --> 00:09:15.836
Before you dash home
and implement this filing system --

00:09:15.860 --> 00:09:17.591
(Laughter)

00:09:17.615 --> 00:09:20.253
it's worth recognizing
that you probably already have.

00:09:20.891 --> 00:09:24.201
(Laughter)

00:09:24.225 --> 00:09:27.091
That pile of papers on your desk ...

00:09:27.115 --> 00:09:29.589
typically maligned
as messy and disorganized,

00:09:29.613 --> 00:09:32.178
a pile of papers is, in fact,
perfectly organized --